    "text": [
        "Dear Sir,",
        "I am writing to apply for the job opening of the manager and came across the opportunity in today\u2019s newspaper dated 16-June-2022. I believe that my experience aligns with the requirements of this role.",
        "Let me explain my current status in more detail. Currently,  I am working as a Manager in hotel sunrise in Shimla from last 3 years and got an appreciation certificate from last two years .Before that, I was working in restaurant in Manali. Moreover, my hometown is Chandigarh and all family members are staying there. Therefore, i am looking job in my city so, I can shift to my place.",
        "",
        "I have an experience of five years in the same field and well-versed with working of restaurant. Hence, I can also handle accounts section and know how to handle customers politely.",
        "I will be available from Thursday to Saturday for interview. I will be more than happy to cooperate during any other times, if these times conflict with your schedule.",
        "I look forward for your positive reply. All experience certificate and resume is attached with this letter.",
        "Yours faithfully,",
        "Peter"
